Investigative Journalist and social media influencer, Fisayo Soyombo has wondered why the recent attack on the Catholic Church in Owo Kingdom is being reported as a bomb blast.
He added that the video circulating on various social media platforms indicates indiscriminate shooting at congregants at a close range.
Recall that some unknown gunmen attacked St. Francis Catholic Church in Owo, Ondo state this morning killing scores of worshippers and many injured. The dastardly act has been condemned by many notable Nigerians including the Governor of Ondo State, Rotimi Akeredolu (SAN).
Fisayo Soyombo, who is known for his outspokenness added that two people who lost their loved ones told him that the victims were shot at.
The recent post by Fisayo Soyombo has generated a lot of reactions from his numerous fans and followers on his verified Facebook page.


